      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in a vehicle that\u2019s built to last! This car is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion, showing some honest wear and tear that comes with a life well-lived. It\u2019s a fantastic, budget-friendly option for someone looking for a dependable driver that still has plenty of miles left to offer. With a bit of TLC, this car is ready for its next chapter with you!",
