    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved, you\u2019ve found it! This car has been my faithful companion and still runs like a dream. It\u2019s in solid shape and ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. It\u2019s not fresh off the lot, but it\u2019s been well-maintained and is super dependable. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come give it a test drive and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
