    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides precise engagement, complemented by a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis retains its signature balance with responsive steering feedback and intact suspension bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust, showing consistent compression across all cylinders and no fluid leaks from the constant pressure valve. A driver-spec machine engineered for performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Reliable engine. Clean interior. Title in hand.",
      "price": 29500.0,
