    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality ride. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, with the original paint holding up well against the elements, save for a few minor chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept strictly smoke-free. The seats offer excellent support with no major tears, and all interior electronics\u2014including the infotainment system, power windows, and dual-zone climate control\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a consistent maintenance schedule. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension provides a comfortable, composed ride over various road surfaces. We recently performed a full fluid check and tire rotation, ensuring this car is ready for the road the moment you turn the key. It is a solid, honest vehicle that delivers a premium feel and peace of mind.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
